plot: As Dreyfuss gets closer to making progress on his mission, important parts of his past come to light. His former partner returns to settle the score from years before and it becomes evident that Dreyfuss' involvement in the supernatural is not something new. Don't miss learning how Malcolm Dreyfuss came to be.

Crane and Diana go to see Dreyfuss about what he's been doing. But before they could get in deeper, someone with mystical powers enters Drefuss' building and seals it off. Crane and Diana confronts him and he reveals himself to be Dreyfuss' former partner whom he betrayed and sent to hell. He returns and is looking for something Dreyfuss has that could restore him. Crane helps Dreyfuss and they take refuge in a safe room. That's when they learn what Dreyfuss he's been doing. Jenny finds a way to stop the man but needs to get in.—rcs0411@yahoo.com
